revisions.description: Latest version of this MIB module.

ciscoDtiExtMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-rfgw10@cisco.com
ciscoDtiExtMIB.description: This MIB module provides the trap objects necessary to monitor the DOCSIS Timing Interface devices.

cdeServerStatusChange.name: cdeServerStatusChange
cdeServerStatusChange.description: A cdeServerStatusChange notification is sent when the DTI Server state changes.

cdeClientStatusChange.name: cdeClientStatusChange
cdeClientStatusChange.description: A cdeClientStatusChange notification is sent when the DTI client state changes.

cdeServerStatusChangeEnable.name: cdeServerStatusChangeEnable
cdeServerStatusChangeEnable.description: This object specifies whether the system produces cdeServerStatusChange notifications. A false value will prevent cdeserverStatusChange notifications from being generated by this system.

cdeClientStatusChangeEnable.name: cdeClientStatusChangeEnable
cdeClientStatusChangeEnable.description: This object specifies whether the system produces cdeClientStatusChange notifications. A false value will prevent cdeClientStatusChange notifications from being generated by this system.

ciscoDtiExtCompliance.name: ciscoDtiExtCompliance
ciscoDtiExtCompliance.description: This is a default module-compliance containing default object groups.

ciscoDtiExtNotifsControlGroup.name: ciscoDtiExtNotifsControlGroup
ciscoDtiExtNotifsControlGroup.description: Contains the group of objects for determining the status of DTI client and server status.

ciscoDtiExtNotifsGroup.name: ciscoDtiExtNotifsGroup
ciscoDtiExtNotifsGroup.description: Contains the group of notification objects for DTI client and server status.
